02:03:48.827 --> 02:03:51.453
I am now gonna read you your rights.

1690
02:03:51.621 --> 02:03:54.832
You have the right to remain silent
and make no statement.

1691
02:03:55.041 --> 02:03:58.335
Any statement can be used against you
in judicial proceedings.

1692
02:04:02.382 --> 02:04:04.633
Captain Phillips. please come in.

1693
02:04:05.885 --> 02:04:07.427
Have a seat.

1694
02:04:08.012 --> 02:04:09.763
Trauma shears.

1695
02:04:10.306 --> 02:04:12.766
I'm Chief O'Brien.
I'll be your corpsman today.

1696
02:04:12.976 --> 02:04:15.310
Can you please tell me
what's going on?

1697
02:04:16.187 --> 02:04:17.938
Can you talk?

1698
02:04:18.106 --> 02:04:20.941
Can you tell me what's going on?
Yeah. Uh... Uh...

1699
02:04:21.109 --> 02:04:22.317
I'm okay.

1700
02:04:22.527 --> 02:04:24.736
Are you okay?
Because you don't look okay.

1701
02:04:24.946 --> 02:04:27.239
Are you in any pain right now?

1702
02:04:28.741 --> 02:04:31.076
Are you in pain right now?
Uh... Uh...

1703
02:04:31.244 --> 02:04:32.911
Right there. on your side.

1704
02:04:33.079 --> 02:04:34.830
Okay. Let me see it really quick.

1705
02:04:35.039 --> 02:04:37.416
Can you lift up your arm?
Does that hurt?

1706
02:04:37.584 --> 02:04:38.959
Little bit?
[VOICE BREAKING] Little bit.

1707
02:04:39.127 --> 02:04:41.461
Is it tender?
Go ahead and put your arm down.

1708
02:04:41.629 --> 02:04:43.630
I need you to look at me.
Calm down.

1709
02:04:43.798 --> 02:04:46.133
and I need you to breathe.
Deep breaths.

1710
02:04:46.301 --> 02:04:47.593
There you go. Very good.

1711
02:04:48.219 --> 02:04:50.387
Awesome.
Now I want you to relax your arm.

1712
02:04:50.597 --> 02:04:53.932
We're gonna put this on.
get your heart rate and oxygen level.

1713
02:04:54.100 --> 02:04:56.059
make sure you're breathing.
Okay.

1714
02:04:56.227 --> 02:04:58.145
I want you to keep
doing that. okay?

1715
02:04:58.313 --> 02:05:00.189
Gonna put this on your finger.

1716
02:05:00.356 --> 02:05:02.566
O'BRIEN:
Can you tell me what happened
to your head?

1717
02:05:02.734 --> 02:05:04.401
MAN:
Put it on your finger.

1718
02:05:04.569 --> 02:05:06.320
Uh... They. uh...

1719
02:05:06.487 --> 02:05:09.239
[STAMMERING]

1720
02:05:09.407 --> 02:05:11.116
O'BRIEN:
It's okay. take your time.

1721
02:05:11.284 --> 02:05:14.578
There's a 2-centimeter laceration
on the left eyebrow.

1722
02:05:14.746 --> 02:05:15.787
[SOBBING]

1723
02:05:15.955 --> 02:05:17.497
It's okay. It's all right.

1724
02:05:17.665 --> 02:05:21.084
Okay. Okay.
I want you to look at me and breathe.

1725
02:05:21.252 --> 02:05:22.294
Understand?
PHILLIPS [IN NORMAL VOICE]: Yeah.

1726
02:05:22.462 --> 02:05:23.754
Okay. all right.

1727
02:05:23.922 --> 02:05:28.592
He's got a 4-centimeter gap.
Little laceration there on the left temple.

1728
02:05:28.760 --> 02:05:30.427
MAN: Got it.
O'BRIEN: Okay. Very good.

1729
02:05:30.595 --> 02:05:32.221
All right.
You're doing great. okay?

1730
02:05:32.430 --> 02:05:35.933
Did all this blood come
from your eyebrow and your head?

1731
02:05:36.559 --> 02:05:37.601
What?

1732
02:05:37.769 --> 02:05:40.479
Did the blood come
from your eyebrow and your head?

1733
02:05:40.647 --> 02:05:42.731
All of this.
Well. no. not all of it.

1734
02:05:42.899 --> 02:05:45.275
O'BRIEN: Okay.
That's not mine.

1735
02:05:45.485 --> 02:05:48.111
O'BRIEN:
Okay. all right. all right.
Look at me.

1736
02:05:48.279 --> 02:05:49.988
We're gonna lay you down.
Okay.

1737
02:05:50.156 --> 02:05:52.241
O'BRIEN: All right.
Yeah.

1738
02:05:52.408 --> 02:05:55.035
I want you to lay down
nice and gently.
Nice and gently.

1739
02:05:55.203 --> 02:05:57.913
Aah.
You're okay. I got you.

1740
02:05:58.331 --> 02:06:00.749
There you go. Very good.
Unh.

1741
02:06:00.917 --> 02:06:02.668
Captain. you're safe now. okay?

1742
02:06:02.835 --> 02:06:05.420
Thank you.
O'BRIEN: You're welcome.

1743
02:06:05.588 --> 02:06:07.297
You're okay.
[VOICE BREAKING] Thank you.

1744
02:06:07.465 --> 02:06:09.007
You're welcome.

1745
02:06:09.175 --> 02:06:12.302
Does my family know?
Your family knows you're safe.

1746
02:06:12.512 --> 02:06:15.931
You'll be able to call them
as soon as you are taken care of.

1747
02:06:16.099 --> 02:06:18.016
[♪♪♪]

1748
02:06:18.226 --> 02:06:20.310
Sir. I need you
to breathe. okay?

1749
02:06:20.478 --> 02:06:23.063
You are safe and you are fine.

1750
02:06:23.856 --> 02:06:25.732
It's gonna be okay.

1751
02:06:26.818 --> 02:06:29.027
Everything's gonna be okay.

1752
02:06:30.530 --> 02:06:32.447
It's gonna be okay.

1753
02:06:36.911 --> 02:06:46.911
[♪♪♪]
